 />\n你行埋一邊咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ad1af265f6eaed21c8442522afc5473fa1c726","tid":294261,"uid":51200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T20:40:26.000Z","msg":"另一方面，d人行得快既城市有個好明顯既特徵，<br />\n就係交通差，又或者條路（不論行人定馬路）都特別窄既城市，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你去過Napoli 一轉就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBudapest 既地鐵扶手電梯又係勁快但又震，<br />\n親身體驗過上斜速度應該係香港at least 1.5倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實全世界都一鳩樣，路窄人多就自然要行快d，<br />\nBarcelona 一樣會有鬼妹撞9人迫上車，<br />\n呢d唔係香港專利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a205588eadf31c9eab157bc3003e8b1dfb78d5e4","tid":294261,"uid":13467,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T20:49:32.000Z","msg":"關歐洲撚事<br />\n你係大陸食狗唔犯法咁你係香港會唔會食<br />\n弱智屌你老母"},{"pid":"c9bdc2d9444f2e9ea930be49cda9cad7b9cfb765","tid":294261,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T21:11:18.000Z","msg":"人多排得耐塞車之類一定會有人屌，<br />\n人多左，道路或者交通系統無upgrade 到係政府問題，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n世界一直變，人一直多，<br />\n當交通系統同道路負荷增至一定水平，而同時間政府又唔做野去令問題改善，<br />\n好自然地，市民就會用自己方法（例如：屌人行得慢），之後形成風氣，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以使用者既角度同能力去抒解返道路擁擠問題，<br />\n向其他道路使用者施加壓力<br />\n加快道路流動性，<br />\n不過歸根究底，都係政府無做好人口丶交通政策等等，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令城市承載力上升到某一層次。<br />\n<br />\n如果你一個城市可以做到有效擴張同人口控制，<br />\n根本唔會有樓主口中既風氣出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}